trans-unit.source: Represents a single [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element in an MSBuild project.
The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> object that represents the <see langword="Task" /> element to add to the <see langword="Target" /> element.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Target" /> 요소에 추가할 <see langword="Task" /> 요소를 나타내는 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified [Task](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d82e2485-e5f0-4936-a357-745bacccc299) element to the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element.
A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> object represents a child <c>Task</c> element of the <c>Target</c> element.
Gets the <c>Condition</c> attribute value of the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element.
The <c>Condition</c> attribute value of the <c>Target</c> element.
Gets the <c>DependsOnTargets</c> attribute value of the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element, which is a semicolon-separated list.
trans-unit.target: [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) 요소의 <c>DependsOnTargets</c> 특성 값을 세미콜론으로 구분된 목록 형태로 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <c>DependsOnTargets</c> attribute value of the <c>Target</c> element.
Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" />.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" />.

This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 사용 하면 호출자가 사용할 수는 `foreach` C# 언어의 (`for each` 에 [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)])는 개인을 반복 하 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> 개체에 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> object represents a child element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> 개체의 자식 요소를 나타냅니다는 `Target` 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the items that are to be input into this target.
trans-unit.target: 이 대상에 입력할 항목을 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the items.
Items inside this target attribute are used as the inputs in the top level dependency analysis.
trans-unit.target: 이 대상 특성 안에 포함 된 항목은 최상위 종속성 분석을 위한 입력으로 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element was imported into the project.
trans-unit.target: [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) 요소를 프로젝트로 가져왔는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <c>Target</c> element was imported into the project; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> 경우는 <c>대상</c> 요소가 고, 그렇지 않으면 프로젝트로 가져온 <see langword="false" />합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <c>Name</c> attribute value of the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element.
The <c>Name</c> attribute value of the <c>Target</c> element.
Gets or sets the expected outputs of this target.
trans-unit.target: 이 대상의 예상 출력을 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the outputs.
You can apply transforms to this target attribute to transform a set of input items into a set of output items.
trans-unit.target: 출력 항목의 집합으로 입력된 항목의 집합을 변환할 대상 특성에는 변환을 적용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is used not only for top level dependency analysis but also for the purposes of defining this targets outputs.
trans-unit.target: 이 특성은 최상위 종속성 분석 뿐만 아니라이 대상 출력을 정의 하는 용도로 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> object that represents the <see langword="Task" /> element to remove from the <see langword="Target" /> element.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Target" /> 요소에서 제거할 <see langword="Task" /> 요소를 나타내는 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified [Task](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d82e2485-e5f0-4936-a357-745bacccc299) element from the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element.
A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> object represents a child `Task` element of the `Target` element.
